

It's simple desktop app using Gnome(Gtk4) under linux ubuntu

Features:
1. Dark-Mode
2. Localization and support English and Arabic
3. add data
4. display data
5. searching
6. Login/Logout

Development features:
1. A protected Login portal screen system with top-aligned toast feedback layouts.
2. Full RTL layout direction toggles linked directly with a dynamic i18n translation engine for instant English/Arabic switches.
3. Real-time in-memory storage array filtering with immediate interface clearances to prevent duplicate data stacking bugs.
4. Optimized, thread-safe background processing workers that prevent system stutters.

You can run the app under linux only.

Install packages
$ sudo apt gnome-builder 
or
$ flatpak install flathub org.gnome.Builder

Run:
python3 main.py
